dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Adam Green. May I have your name, please?
Hi Adam, my name is Olivia King.
Nice to meet you, Olivia. How can I assist you today?
I'd like to file a new claim after a recent accident.
Of course, Olivia. In order to process the claim, I will need your policy number and the date of the accident.
My policy number is seven one two four six and the accident happened on the sixth of September.
Thank you for providing that information, Olivia. I will start the claim process right away.
Great, thank you so much for your help.
You're welcome, Olivia. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that will be all for now. Thank you, Adam.
Thank you for reaching out to Old Stone Auto Insurance, Olivia. Have a great day!
